<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
FOOTBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS; SAN FRANCISCO 49ERS (FOOTBALL TEAM); MINNESOTA VIKINGS 
(FOOTBALL TEAM); MONTANA, JOE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
